text: The Nissan Qashqai is a car produced by Nissan. It replaced the models Nissan Almera, Nissan Primera and Nissan Terrano II in 2007. The model is produced in Sunderland in the UK and is a popular car there, it was facelifted in 2010 and entered its second generation in 2014. The third generation launched in 2021. == Engines == * 1.6 84 kW (114 hp) and 86 kW (117 hp) * 2.0 104 kW (141 hp) * 1.5 dCi 76 kW (103 hp) and 81 kW (110 hp) * 2.0 dCi 110 kW (150 hp) Qashqai Category:Front wheel drive vehicles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
title: Nissan Qashqai
